&lt;h3&gt;将Hextra设置为Git子模块&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;将hextra设置为git子模块&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%e5%b0%86hextra%e8%ae%be%e7%bd%ae%e4%b8%bagit%e5%ad%90%e6%a8%a1%e5%9d%97&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h4&gt;先决条件&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;先决条件-1&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
